# Chatbot frontend (Vite)

# ── Local dev (`cd frontend && npm run dev`) ──
# Leave VITE_API_URL unset → `/chat` and `/api` use Vite proxy to http://127.0.0.1:3000 (override with VITE_DEV_PROXY_TARGET in shell or .env — see frontend/vite.config.js).

# ── Production build on same host as API ──
# Leave VITE_API_URL unset → relative `/chat` (monolith).

# ── Widget hosted on a different origin than the API ──
# Production default is in `frontend/.env.production` (Vercel). Override locally with:
# VITE_API_URL=https://master-watch-yv9c.vercel.app

# If backend is not on port 3000 during dev, set for Vite proxy only:
# VITE_DEV_PROXY_TARGET=http://127.0.0.1:4000
